Hours of Operation Friday and Saturday 11:30am to 11pm Sunday through Thursday 11:30am to 10pm PICKUP HOURS Monday through Sunday 11:30 am - 9:00pm Order For Pickup Order for Delivery Rum River Come by land or sea, all are welcome. Rum River Bar and Grill is part of Catches and has the biggest, tallest, largest tiki hut around. Even the shape of this tiki hut is different from the others you see. Park the car and mosey up to Rum River Bar and Grill. Our Florida beach bar sits on the shores of the "Cottee" River. You can while away your day at this Florida beach bar. Order some Grouper Cousins, a cold beer and relax on the shores of this quiet and charming river. On the weekends you can catch a live band. Friday and Saturday night the bands start at 7 PM and on Sundays there is live music in the afternoon. Rum River Bar and Grill believes the key to a great beach bar, even if it is on the river, is live music. Of course, good food and cold drinks are important too. Rum River features a diverse menu with a large selection of appetizers, sandwiches and entrees, play area for the kids and is boat accessible.
